{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"733f99fe99","title":"戚本禹刘建勋接见河南各方代表谈话纪要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"07e34506c9","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":14,"articleId":"733f99fe99","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"大联合","id":"18bf6a78fe","type":"主题"},{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"刘建勋","id":"3ae36abefb","type":"人物"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革办事组","id":"5823a9918f","type":"人物"},{"name":"叶群","id":"62ff3f0cef","type":"人物"},{"name":"文敏生","id":"9047f04de9","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"7115a65a26","name":"刘建勋"},{"id":"9014e20fdf","name":"戚本禹"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"71b4f342e3","type":"title","text":"戚本禹刘建勋接见河南各方代表谈话纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b1615b4844","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：1967年7月14日晚10点10分，地点：人大会堂南会议室。出席：二七公社，河造总，十大总部各五名代表，郑大战斗师一名代表，中央文革办事组同志，军区动员处参谋。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f982f94f33","type":"paragraph","text":"从西苑旅社上车时，河造总一代表强行上车，无理取闹，被文革办事组的同志赶下车来……，戚本禹同志未来之前，只有刘建勋同志在会议室，我二七代表与刘建勋同志进行了亲切的交谈。我代表向刘建勋同志汇报河造总放火烧了二七公社8·16大楼。三厂、五厂省工总赶我工人出厂，工人被打，被抓；陈副司令员从北京回去被铁军扣住等严重情况时，建勋同志甚为关切。问：“是否报给了中央，戚本禹同志知道吗？”……几十分钟后，戚本禹同志派人把刘建勋同志叫去。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a848bc0660","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹（以下简称戚）：你们三方协议达成了吗？谈得怎么样？（看名单）张宝怀你谈一下吧。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86ed43a4ff","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：两天来我们谈了两次。第一次会谈，铁军有意转移主题，谈郑州武斗；第二次河造总又是如此，而且，某些组织一再拖延时间，因此，正式协议没达成一条。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be481e2321","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总（辩解）：不是那样，有几个方面达成了。二七冲我们批判文敏生的大会，今晚还调动几千人，围我省一技校红造联。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bd73da0af7","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：刚才河造总提的问题，在今天协议会上已经提过了。会后我们挂长途电话进行了核实，两个事都纯属造谣，并无此事。挑起武斗，放火杀人并非别人，是河造总，省工总。我七中8·16大楼被河造总省一技校的红造联放火烧了，几十名红卫兵被迫跳楼，三厂、五厂的二七工人被打伤几十人。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c3a478d0c0","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：跳楼的红卫兵死了没有，伤了没有？","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"82d0df4151","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：伤了几十人，死的还正在调查，现在还不清楚。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc78281b17","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：烧的七中“8·16”？","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"329da1077d","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：是。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"294483dbe3","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：是谁放的火？","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fb52eb19bb","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：是围楼的人，是河造总的。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5d0a74aece","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：是他们自己放火烧的。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5c9529f17f","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：楼上的人是谁？","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bc52f0f2c5","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：二七公社七中“8·16”的。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"872ddd9fbd","type":"paragraph","text":"戚（对河造总）：他们自己烧自己？我就不相信！","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0beed52530","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：是他们放的火。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b59cad607a","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：二七公社自己烧自己的人，这个事情（转对秘书）你快去查查，打长途电话，问我们的记者。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ecc7c09a9f","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你谈，是谁烧的楼。","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"599ea05cb3","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：今天上午11点火才熄灭，他们浇了汽油，还加上木材，当时卫戍司令部、军区都去了人，开去了两部救火车，他们不让救，把车推跑了。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d59fd13086","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：谁推的？","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2ab53fd057","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：围楼的人。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8f5887b0fb","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：谁围的？","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ec4143c4c","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：河造总省一技校红造联。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c328ad1ec","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：是他们自己烧的。","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f2c71f994d","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：他们的楼，他们自己烧，我们的人民大会堂，自己烧。哪有这样的事！你这样说谎话不行啊！你们自己达成的协议，自己撕毁。","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6b61f69f92","type":"paragraph","text":"铁军：我们五天之内两个战士被杀，一少年铁军黄××被二七骗去，……另一个也是二七（铁军说二七杀了他们两个人）","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3273f5eb41","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：这个事情我们也进行了充分的调查，一个是铁军互相打架时打死的，一个是河造总打死的，与我二七无关。","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b21e755c5e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（问铁军）你说都是二七打的？","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73020976e3","type":"paragraph","text":"铁军：（吞吞吐吐）嗯，就是。","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"20b96d7099","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你要调查清楚，你不要说这个问题，我问你，你听没听说你们把陈副司令员绑架了？","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"395024fd77","type":"paragraph","text":"铁军：没听说。","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c80c3319bc","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：怎么没听说，光听说那一方面的（指他们造谣说二七打了他们的人），就没听说这方面的。这么大的事，你就不知道？","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d87107994","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：（又站起来说二七公社的坏话）","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"424223b80b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（对河造总）你说的是陈副司令员的事情吗？你知道陈副司令员被关了吗？","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94bc45b0bf","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：不是，我们不知道。","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1efe3ddb8b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：这么大的事情，你们都不知道？","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d4c3ee66f9","type":"paragraph","text":"造总：……（无言）","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dd8570fea4","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：军区来人没有？","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1ab6369103","type":"paragraph","text":"杨松峰（军区的）：来了。","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5960840431","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你听说没有？","index":41,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"60194ed997","type":"paragraph","text":"杨：这个人确实是死了。","index":42,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a82cfbecab","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你说什么？！怎么死了？！","index":43,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5c729582a2","type":"paragraph","text":"杨：（目瞪口呆的摇头）嗯……","index":44,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"02bedab745","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：我问你陈副司令员的事情，你说的是什么？","index":45,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d7da9ef73","type":"paragraph","text":"杨：（恍然大悟）啊，我说是刚才铁军说的那个事情。","index":46,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c3fe724414","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：我问你陈副司令员的事，你听说没有？","index":47,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"10af4e7eb5","type":"paragraph","text":"杨：我来的时候还没听说，到这里才听说。","index":48,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7970427972","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：这么大的事情，你们的司令员你就不关心，你自己的司令员被绑架了你都不知道？！你是干什么的？！谁的秘书？","index":49,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d0ff6e1944","type":"paragraph","text":"杨：我是参谋。","index":50,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1ac5806bd","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：谁的参谋。","index":51,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bd188d5cce","type":"paragraph","text":"杨：动员处的参谋。","index":52,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bd16d56d61","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你是跟谁来的？跟何运洪吗？","index":53,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ba7ef4c0d8","type":"paragraph","text":"杨：嗯，是工作人员。","index":54,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3da1681e0f","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：工作人员来几个？","index":55,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1ba6aa6810","type":"paragraph","text":"杨：来六个。","index":56,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ade2bd499","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你回去跟何运洪讲一下，他要求让陈桂昌回郑州，我们同意，但他又不给他（指陈桂昌司令员）任何安全保证。","index":57,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7c17ed68fc","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：不但陈副司令员，所有支持二七的军区首长，都没有安全保障。公安厅高大同也被绑架走了。","index":58,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"508561a96b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：陈桂昌是好同志，是军区中支左的好同志，陈桂昌你们说让回去，我们同意，回去了又不加保证，你们搞什么名堂？我很怀疑。","index":59,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5c7fcf56ee","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（问铁军）你能代表铁军吗？","index":60,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"718c5b2106","type":"paragraph","text":"铁军：能，但这个事我不知道。","index":61,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"974e9f1c29","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你怎么只关心一方面的，怎么不关心另一方面的？","index":62,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8436878047","type":"paragraph","text":"铁军：如果是我们干的，保证马上放出，并作检查。","index":63,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"99998fce8c","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们要保证陈副司令员的安全，要打电话回去。","index":64,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3dcbdbd091","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：（送焦作电报）","index":65,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b0d23f4b17","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：这是陈桂昌的吗？","index":66,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f5d2fcf3dc","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：不是，是焦作来的电报。","index":67,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3bf60f7394","type":"paragraph","text":"造总：（造谣说二七围了他们省一技校红造联）","index":68,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9cb11a1a3d","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（看二七代表送去的河造总的造谣传单）你们这里来的都是协商文件的吗？","index":69,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a56c43767","type":"paragraph","text":"十大总部：我们有的不是，来时是点名。","index":70,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cef92f69c7","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：点名，谁点名？","index":71,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e1d1e1b06","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：我们全是。","index":72,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0d19e9b8fc","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们中间有参加达协议的吗？","index":73,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5ac1d26687","type":"paragraph","text":"十大总部、河造总回答：有。","index":74,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1ec11287ef","type":"paragraph","text":"（二七代表把军区副司令员刘大坤7月10日的讲话，河造总铅印的传单送给戚）","index":75,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"20f59a27d6","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：军区动员河造总，7月10日在郑州市体育场，开了一个几万农民大会，还大搞经济主义，刘大坤代表河南军区发言，坚决支持河造总。","index":76,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"45b96f28fe","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：军区的同志，有这个事呀？","index":77,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9e00d4d162","type":"paragraph","text":"军区：有。","index":78,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a8bd79e6d4","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：这是那个人的讲话？","index":79,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bef901f0d8","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：刘大坤。","index":80,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4c7dd34cc0","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：刘大坤是什么人？","index":81,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e9260f913","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：河南军区副司令员，跳得可高。","index":82,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b12e09de55","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（从头到尾很快地看了一遍刘大坤讲话的传单）这个讲话是错误的。嗯嗯，是错误的，是不符合中央精神的，你回去和何运洪讲一下。（对军区）这个是对抗中央指示的，这和你们军区的检讨精神完全相反。你们一方面在北京检讨，一方面副司令员在家作这个报告，这个报告倾向性是很清楚的，我要求你们对这个东西要做出说明，你们认为正确的还是错误的，另外，对怎么开的那个会，你们要写个说明。","index":83,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c8360977e5","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：我上次接总理指示，7月4日到郑州解决铁路停车问题，接触到钟政委，董参谋长，他们都说：我们现在、过去、将来都是坚决支持河造总的，从来没说过支持二七。","index":84,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"401ce5c834","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（抬手，手中拿刘大坤讲话传单）这个文件和讲话（指政委）有关，你（指秘书）念一下中央文件，（这个文件和郑州农民开会有关，提到河南了。）","index":85,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8d63c8c0d4","type":"paragraph","text":"秘书：（念）中共中央文件，中发……","index":86,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b55a03c6ad","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你念一遍，我给各个组织一份，下去抄一下。","index":87,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d2d729534","type":"paragraph","text":"秘书：（念完文件）","index":88,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"af488d5392","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：我们坚决拥护，坚决执行，坚决捍卫中央决定。","index":89,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1382419d56","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：（发牢骚，仍想攻击二七公社）","index":90,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dadc6bd5c0","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（对河造总）你看，二七表示坚决贯彻执行了嘛！你们呢？","index":91,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"af33c02692","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：（慌忙地改为）我……我们也坚决……／","index":92,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"845668f4a6","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：要不折不扣地执行嘛。文件上点了河南的名，河南的这个事情。","index":93,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f84f8a5b6","type":"paragraph","text":"（他们纷纷表态）","index":94,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6aac56ab7f","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：大家都要执行，农民还有生产任务嘛，让他们进城，还给他们工分，谁给呢？（给军区文件一份）文件要带回去。现在是不是集中起来协商问题？","index":95,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc9c10ad79","type":"paragraph","text":"铁总：（十总之一）我讲一点，铁路停车……","index":96,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fde580a535","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：这应当由谁来负责，谁搞的？","index":97,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dd9fd22849","type":"paragraph","text":"铁总：我们认为……","index":98,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"47761df5f9","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：这个事情和我们的看法差不多，不光是洛阳的，这里面有问题，我正在调查。","index":99,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f5b037742","type":"paragraph","text":"铁总：这是安阳的报告，和我们调查基本相符。","index":100,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"10d1976e21","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：这执行中央决定，不要拦车嘛。","index":101,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1bdec07ec1","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：二七在信阳、南阳地区搞了个九条，六条，说是中央文件。","index":102,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2306c38dff","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：谁搞的？","index":103,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9794e6ef73","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：二七公社。","index":104,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"83c45ba702","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（那张传单）是不是根据传达搞的，是不是军区在中央的检讨搞的，河南“军区犯了方向性、路线性错误”，这也符合中央意思，不过不能公开地乱写传单。","index":105,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f76b0a041c","type":"paragraph","text":"省工总：（立即起来要说）二七……","index":106,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cbc9e5d13d","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你坐下，你是工人总部的，你说人家，看看你们的。那天我和你们谈了一次，你们就发传单，你们说我承认你们是造反派。那天我批评你嘛，批评你们保军区的错误路线，没有谈及到你们组织问题。","index":107,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ff2c25f6a7","type":"paragraph","text":"省工总：我们没有搞。","index":108,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"560541f750","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：不是你们的？反正是那天来的嘛。你们这样做，正是硬逼着我们说你们是什么性质的嘛！叫我们对你们的组织表态嘛！你们想想这对你们有什么好处！我对你们工人总部是有希望的，你要说我们承认了你们是造反派，硬要逼着我们表态，你叫我们怎么办？对工人我还是不愿意说那样的话的。不太愿意说你们是老保希望你们改正错误的，对你们有希望但我们是有原则性的。","index":109,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"939d597ab4","type":"paragraph","text":"你们二七也不要把工人总部说成老保。工人嘛，只要起来造反，不分早晚，都可以嘛！我们要欢迎。十大总部是不一样的，公安总部是保守的，省直总部有问题很复杂。有坏人操纵的，对待工人嘛不要说人家保了军区的错误路线，就说人家老保。中央没有这样说嘛！你们这样很不利于团结。工人同志嘛大多数是好的，受些黑修养的影响，有的也是一时弄不清楚，有的有私心杂念，犯些错误，但不要看太严重了。不要叫人家老保。如果他们坚持错误么可以斗争；但要讲究方式。只要人家不再支持军区的错误路线愿意起来革命，我们应该欢迎，不应该叫人家老保。","index":110,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"32e26f0d98","type":"paragraph","text":"省工总：我们有个初步检查想表一下态。","index":111,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"014beebaef","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：好嘛。","index":112,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb8f189aa7","type":"paragraph","text":"省工总：（对刘建勋、何运洪、公安总部、二七公社等问题作了一些检查）","index":113,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"555a54236c","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你和家里商量了没有？","index":114,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f0ddad44a9","type":"paragraph","text":"省工总：我们和家里说了，家里还作了修改。","index":115,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"422cec04e2","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：建勋同志，你听了没有，有些问题当然是他们认识问题。但总的态度还是比较好的，你们对二七公社还要再提高一些。二七公社是革命造反派嘛，有个别组织不纯，总是难免的，恐怕你们那个组织也不纯吧，你们就那么纯？我就不相信。康老说了嘛，二七公社造反派。总理也说了嘛，二七公社造反派。当时军区的错误路线谁在抵制？二七公社，还有八·二四嘛。但是现在肯定他们了，他们又骄傲了，内部又闹分裂闹风头。（这时服务员进来对戚说：叶群同志给你来电话）你们等一下，我们出去一下。","index":116,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"84b594ec6c","type":"paragraph","text":"（刘建勋和我代表谈话，一会戚本禹回来）","index":117,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce2d031f39","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们谈好了吗？","index":118,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1fc88e450e","type":"paragraph","text":"省工总：最近我们有个希望，希望刘建勋同志去主持三结合。","index":119,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd64eedf4f","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（对建勋）过去他们反你，现在要求你回去，这很好嘛！（对省工总）建勋有些缺点和错误，但能主动地迅速检查和改正这很好嘛！中央是信任的，你们呢？","index":120,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aa55ac26d1","type":"paragraph","text":"省工总：坚决支持，坚决拥护。","index":121,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"749a0c8470","type":"paragraph","text":"战斗师：坚决支持。","index":122,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ad4d321b55","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们二七不要讲了，你们是很支持刘建勋的。","index":123,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"42baef031a","type":"paragraph","text":"财贸：（谈协议）","index":124,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40c8b57416","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：省工总还表个态，你们呢？","index":125,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0bc7a290c7","type":"paragraph","text":"财贸：我们上次写了个东西，已经交给你了。","index":126,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80dd335c88","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：联络员同志，把省工总和他们的那个东西印出来发给大家，二七公社都发表声明了嘛。","index":127,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2adb5c3ad7","type":"paragraph","text":"财贸：我们最近总部服务组提了几条意见。","index":128,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e46e4f7300","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们“二七”，我们刚才讲过了，你们过去是受压制的。但是现在肯定了你们，你们对待其他组织会不会象“赵太爷”那样，不许人家起来革命？你们的那三个缺点还是存在的。（秘书将长途电话调查七中“8．16”情况交给戚，戚看后）你（秘书）把这个给大家念一下。","index":129,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f8ec615ed4","type":"paragraph","text":"秘书念：我们的记者来电，事情是这样的，铁军×××在图书馆里看书。七中另一学生×××去偷书。×××不让×××偷，×××就拿起火钳照×××背心刺去，×××受重伤，医疗无效死去。铁军造谣编说“二七”公社给打死的，但这两个人都不是“二七”公社的。这样就以“二七”公社七中“8．16”打死人为借口，河造总省一技校红造联等包围了七中“二七”公社“8．16”战士，并放火烧楼。楼上主要是“二七”公社的战士。另外粮食干校也发生了武斗，放火烧大楼了，也说是“二七”公社烧的。","index":130,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb32ac2d88","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：这回清楚了吗？放火的人你不要认为找不着他，等两个月后以后，我们腾出手来，总可以找到他。那要处理的，那一派也不行。","index":131,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"539b033b9a","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：我们回去马上调查清楚。","index":132,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3123264fa8","type":"paragraph","text":"造总：（无奈，只好承认）我们回去立即查清。","index":133,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ef8152569b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们是不是尽快地搞个协议，不要搞的太繁琐了。你们“二七”不是搞了个声明，你们都可以搞一个嘛！十大总部今后不要叫十大总部八大总部，因为这里边有区别的嘛。公安公社很坏，省委总部有问题，我看有坏人操纵。是不是就几个大的问题，各摆一下观点，就其目的达成一个协议。个别问题回来再说。不要复杂，订上几条，比如军区是不是方向路线错误？这方面是不是可以达成协议，你们怎么看？另一条对省委走资本主义道路当权派，究竟谁是走资本主义道路的当权派，是文敏生，赵文甫，还是刘建勋？第三，对刘建勋支持还是反对？","index":134,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e1880c4211","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：关于省委当权派问题，经过两次协商，第一次协商时，除河造总刘介廷对杨蔚屏态度暧昧外，所有其他代表的发言都坚决打倒赵、文、杨，本来可以达成协议，但是有的人保……","index":135,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ac643a232","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（摆手）可以了，可以了，杨蔚屏达不成，可以写个文敏生，赵文甫等一小撮嘛！这一“等”就进去了。另外，是二七公社，（对河造总和十大总部）过去你们抓人家的人，中央认为他是革命造反派，你们不同意，达成协议，是革命造反派（对其他代表）你们怎么看？同意就达成，不同意就算。","index":136,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"70e3a8c77c","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：我们同意，二七公社是革命造反派。","index":137,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cff788df64","type":"paragraph","text":"新乡李玉坤：我们同意二七公社是革命造反派……","index":138,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e94b31e5f","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：二七公社有几个缺点，我们已经和他们讲了，为什么要肯定，如果不肯定，抵制军区的错误路线怎么体现，怎么叫方向路线错误呢？“二七”抵制了军区的错误路线，军区镇压了群众，他们抓了“二七”那么多人。","index":139,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1f8f7b75f1","type":"paragraph","text":"新乡李××：耿其昌也抓了人。","index":140,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"82030d2763","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：耿的事慢慢来，能达成就达成，有几条写几条，不行回来再说，搞个补充协定，第三次补充协定都可以么。","index":141,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"67b8202c9d","type":"paragraph","text":"铁总：我们希望铁路总三派坐在一起，搞个协议。","index":142,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3664479029","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：那好嘛！你们“二七”的也有人吗？","index":143,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0c5dc3ce10","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：有。","index":144,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"adfebe972e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们铁路三方面有多少人？","index":145,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ec36841728","type":"paragraph","text":"铁总：我们一万一千人，河造总三千人，“二七”一千人。","index":146,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c630c77db","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：不对，我们九千多人。","index":147,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"61af7ec232","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：我们成立了铁路工人公社，可能有一万人。（吵）","index":148,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b9c7dee0e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（对“二七”）人家一说你们人少，你们就沉不住气了，说你们人多。你说你们的人多？我才不相信呢！人少才是实际，因为都反对你们嘛！谁敢参加！真理不在于人多。马、恩他们开始只有两个人，后来发展了，就我们中国有六、七亿。除地、富、反、坏、右外。不在乎人多，看你们方向对不对。你方向不对，就不能代表真理，人多也是庞然大物。","index":149,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a002f2ff35","type":"paragraph","text":"铁总：我们三派分歧不大，从未武斗过。首长给我们提供大联合方便。","index":150,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4a0cb6019e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们三派协商吧！我支持好不好？军区准备作了检讨，写个声明，这个声明支持造反派了，但也没说哪个人是保守的。出来之后我看见了。二七公社你们过去是受压制的。他们发出之后，你们要欢迎。军区有两面派，我现在当着军区的面这样说，你们革命派要进行斗争。但方法要注意。两面派是暂时的，广大的干部是要跟毛主席走的。如果有人，不管是军区的，还是省委的，还要搞些花样，你们要斗争。另外，不要以为结合你们，你们就认为当上官了，不要官官相护。如果有两面派就要不含糊地进行斗争，不能没有原则。两面派不怕刘建勋，也不怕中央文革，就怕群众造他的反，他一出来群众就揪他。也许没有，有待考查。相当复杂，斗争远远没有结束，现大才刚刚开始，要有个准备。不要太紧，一急事就不好办了。是不是今天就到这里，下面我还有事。","index":151,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"48a2ddcc91","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：是不是一军（野战军。开封驻军）的我们也搞一下。","index":152,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"432d9dac3d","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：“八·二四”与井冈山，你们是不是关于一军的问题，也协议一下。你们是否除几个协议外，也能关于一军的问题达成个协议。洛阳的来了没有？","index":153,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8710b45ac9","type":"paragraph","text":"洛阳：我是“十一”战团的，观点和河造总差不多。洛阳也有三派。","index":154,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"573dd3935c","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：现在搞罢工、拦车的就是你们吗？","index":155,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ab1bf4f65","type":"paragraph","text":"洛阳：不是。","index":156,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c5ce333d5b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：那是哪一派？","index":157,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"abb78a119d","type":"paragraph","text":"洛阳十大总部：也不是我们。","index":158,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb044ad3dc","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：洛阳“八·一六”来了没有？（没有）","index":159,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"83b6b6667c","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：怎么没有让他们来？（指办事组）","index":160,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3378b0c08b","type":"paragraph","text":"办事组：总理办公室打电话，只让通知那一派，没让通知“八·一六”。","index":161,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bcee647274","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：我写了个条总理批示，让三方面都来。总理不是在那上面批示了吗？要“八·一六”来同样的代表。你没看总理的批示吗？","index":162,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8f90b09dbd","type":"paragraph","text":"办事组：看见了。总理值班室打电话说没通知“八·一六”。","index":163,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"56d8903480","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你按文字的东西，不要按电话嘛！要通知他们来。你看什么时候能来？","index":164,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f136753edc","type":"paragraph","text":"办事组：明天通知他们来。","index":165,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e50088661d","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：这里的代表，加上新来的，组成洛阳代表团。怎么组好，你们看。我们要见他们一面。你看还有什么问题？建勋同志还有什么问题？你再和他们扯一扯。","index":166,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a5b75d4da","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：（指中央文件）让我们带一份回去。","index":167,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a8f02974b4","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：可以。以后交给联络员。","index":168,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"711c0f2feb","type":"paragraph","text":"开封“八·二四”：我们开封也搞个协议。","index":169,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"69a3b3701f","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：好吧！试试看，搞不出来再说。","index":170,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5d6ba74229","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（对工人，我们要求你，再给我们读一次）你们，我不谈过了吗？刘建勋同志，你也可以和他们接触接触。你们要尽快地达成协议，中央好批。你们来的时间不短了，你们要回去了。解决了一个问题就前进了一步。现在中央就等着你们的协议。","index":171,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a6b80ce4e5","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：我们要求戚本禹同志单独接见“二七”代表。","index":172,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ad67c21e5b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：好！好！","index":173,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ec09826049","type":"paragraph","text":"铁总、财贸：我们也要求……","index":174,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8528c8bf96","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：让建勋同志接见你们嘛！","index":175,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2cfc5e0c81","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：好么？今后见面还很多。叫我回河南，我同意。我参加了两次会议。我看双方过分对立了。观点可以不同，连人数都对不到一块。大家要冷静下来，要坚持真理，错了就改嘛！就到这里散会好不好？","index":176,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee03ffe519","type":"paragraph","text":"工总、财贸：再说几句吧！我们很愿意听。","index":177,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bd94ed6de8","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：以后我还要分别和你们谈话嘛！好不好？","index":178,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"733f99fe99","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}